{"id":"shealtiel","term":"Shealtiel","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Asked for of God, father of Zerubbabel (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 3:2\">Ezra 3:2</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 3:8\">8</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:1\">Neh. 12:1</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 3:2","Ezra 3:8","Nehemiah 12:1"]}